This is an interactive Rock Paper Scissors game built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript. Play against an AI opponent, track scores, and reset anytime!

---------------------------- Features-----------------------------
- 🎮 Player vs. Computer Gameplay
- 🏆 Score Tracking System
- ✨ Animated Winner Highlight
- 🔊 Sound Effects for Clicks
- 🔄 Reset Functionality

------------------------- How to Play---------------------------------
1. Click **Rock**, **Paper**, or **Scissors** to make your choice.
2. The computer randomly selects an option.
3. The winner is determined based on classic game rules.
4. Click **Reset** to start fresh.

---------------------Show Technologies Used-------------------------
Technologies Used
- HTML 🏗️
- CSS 🎨
- JavaScript ⚡

-------------------------Future Enhancements-------------------------
- 🔹 Add Winning Streak Tracker
